title: DDFP 336: Big trades & free agency
itunes:title: DDFP 336: Big trades & free agency
description:
Shek is joined by Bucky Brooks to discuss Jimmy Graham going to the Seahawks and the Eagles swapping Nick Foles for Sam Bradford. Plus, how do the early free agency moves impact the AFC playoff picture? Lastly, running back Justin Forsett joins the show to discuss his options and relationship with Marshawn Lynch.
